                3. Add authentication pipeline to your router
              </div>
            </div>
            
<!-- Source Citation -->
            <div class="text-xs opacity-70 ml-12 -mt-2">
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                class="w-3 h-3 inline"
                fill="none"
